fields.title: Bracket-Books (Beta)
fields.summary: A Web-app and mobile-friendly cloud based accounting ERP package based on double entry system with GST Billing, Reporting tools, Stock-keeping.
fields.description:
Access your business analytics from your devices anywhere, anytime, anyplace with the power of cloud based storage. We are hosted with the worlds best cloud service providers to provide you the ultimate speed and experience.

we have partnered with a huge community of professionals to serve you from your own town, state or locality for each professional necessity at reasonable rates. Find and hire the best professional near you.

Business data is mostly on physical paper and its a pain to record them , costs incurred on basic vouching with the professionals help and the hours wasted. we bring the power of OCR for invoices, vouchers, notes in one dashboard.

fields.title: Bracket-OCR for Books (Beta)
fields.summary: An AI based OCR enabled dashboard that integrates seamlessly with your accounting ERP package for any type of vouchers, bills and manual data entry.
fields.description:
An AI based OCR enabled dashboard that integrates seamlessly with your accounting ERP package for any type of vouchers, bills and manual data entry for you and your team that can be trained with previous data or used with pre-trained data to automatically record transactions.

Save more than 75% time that your employees use to just record data from plain bills. Let the AI work for you in an efficient manner.

fields.title: Bracket-QRStock (Beta)
fields.summary: Create QR code billing mechanism for all your stock and record all stock keeping with QR codes that can be scanned by any camera scanner.
fields.description:
Create QR code billing mechanism for all your stock and record all stock keeping with QR codes that can be scanned by any camera scanner. Let your billing be efficient if you have a lot of bills to generate on a daily basis and assign a QR code to each stock item with one button.

Manage Codes through our unified dashboard and print them with ease .

Let your customers scan the QR codes with your embedded messages on the QR code for genuine, safe and brand credibility.

Let your billing manager easily scan QR codes and assigning them to bills that integrates directly into the accounting ERP System.

fields.title: Bracket-GST-Pro (Coming Soon)
fields.summary: An Auditors tools that helps reconcile GST data directly from the GSTN portal and match errors and missing entries to avoid tax penalties efficiently.
fields.description:
An Auditors tools that helps reconcile GST data directly from the GSTN portal and match errors and missing entries to avoid tax penalties efficiently.

Match B2B, B2C, credit notes, Debit Notes, e-waybill invioces from across GSTR-1,GSTR-2 and the totals of GSTR-3B with clicks of a single button .

Allow seamless flow of data between GSTN and the accounting ERP package to save data entry time.

Generate reports to pass on to your clients and easily maintain records of discrepancies.

fields.title: Bracket-Ecommerce (Comming Soon)
fields.summary: Create a B2C E-commerce portal directly linked to your accounting ERP stock management data with advanced dashboards and marketing analysis tools.
fields.description:
Create a B2C E-commerce portal directly linked to your accounting ERP stock management data with advanced dashboards and marketing analysis tools. 

Analyse customer behavior, promote your products across the web or social media with built in packages.
